# Metadata And SEO

Every new page should include clear metadata.

## Rules

- Define meaningful `metadata` for layouts/pages (`title`, `description`) when adding routes.
- Keep titles specific to the page content; avoid placeholders.
- Keep descriptions concise and user-focused.
- Revisit metadata when page purpose changes significantly.
- Ensure navigation labels and section headings align with metadata intent.

## For this project

- Keep branding consistent with "Grateful Orange".
